powering knowledge for global dementia awareness - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="ComplyPlus LMS™: Empowering knowledge for global dementia awareness - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-144_"/><p class="sc-jUosCB eIJFN pf-145_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by YuriArcursPeopleimages via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-jUosCB eIJFN pf-147_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">In addition to RAD, several other charities in the UK are dedicated to fighting dementia. These organisations are vital in raising awareness, conducting research, and providing support services. Race Against Dementia Day 2024 is a day of hope, unity, and action. It's an opportunity for individuals, communities, and organisations to come together and work towards a cure for dementia.<br><br>By participating, donating, or spreading the word, you contribute to the global effort to win the race against dementia. Join the race, make a difference, and help beat dementia faster. Together, we can achieve great things and end this devastating disease.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-18d3" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-hAcGzb jHOovW pf-165_ pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-eGPXGI cIlovf"><div class="sc-iCfMLu eehqFj pf-78_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-XxNYO eWQzGj pf-79_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cZMNgc bNHzPH pf-80_">Related blog articles</h3><p class="sc-jUosCB eIJFN pf-82_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Click on the links below to read more articles from our team:</p><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-jHkVzv gbyaRg pf-84_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf